<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta name="viewport"
	content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0" />
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>掌上医生审签系统操作说明</title>
<link href="css/operationNotice.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<script src="/dssweb/js/desktop/jquery/jquery.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="js/operationNotice.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="downloadBar">
		<div id="winningImage">
			<image id="wnImage"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/downloadBar.gif">
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="downloadMiddle">
		<div id="signImage">
			<image id="sgImage" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/sign.gif">
			<div id="downLoad">
				<span>立即下载</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- 操作说明 -->

	<div id="notice">
		<div id="noticeWord" class="noticeWord">操作说明:</div>
		<div id="noticeFirst" class="noticeStep">1.下载与安装</div>
		<div id="noticeSecond" class="noticeStep">2.用户登录</div>
		<div id="noticeThird" class="noticeStep">3.医网签认证证书管理</div>
		<div id="noticeForth" class="noticeStep">4.待审签内容的签名和驳回</div>
		<div id="noticeFifth" class="noticeStep">5.已审签内容的查询</div>
	</div>

	<!--下载与安装  -->

	<div id="downLoadNotice">
		<div name="return" class="noticeWord">
			<返回 操作说明:
		</div>
		<div class="title">下载与安装</div>
		<div class="word">1.请点击上方“立即下载”按钮进入下载页面</div>
		<div id="imgFirst">
			<image class="img"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/download.png">
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- 用户登录 -->

	<div id="userLogin">
		<div name="return" class="noticeWord">
			<返回 操作说明:
		</div>
		<div id="loginTitle" class="title">用户登录</div>
		<div class="word">1.打开App，点击开始使用按钮</div>
		<div id="imgFirst">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/start.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="word">2.输入医生站的工号，以及对应的密码</div>
		<div id="imgFirst">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/login.jpg">
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- 医网签认证证书管理  -->

	<div id="certificate">
		<div name="return" class="noticeWord">
			<返回 操作说明:
		</div>
		<div id="certificateTitle" class="title">医网签认证证书管理</div>
		<div class="word">一、证书管理</div>
		<div class="word">1、下载证书：（下载证书过程仅适用于审核申请通过的用户首次进行下载证书操作）</div>
		<div class="word">（1）下载证书：打开业务App，点击上方医网签入口</div>
		<div id="imgSecond">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/incerti.jpg">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/access.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="word">（2）跳转到医网签证书下载页面，点击“证书管理”中的证书下载进行下载证书操作。</div>
		<div id="imgSecond">
			<image class="imgCerti"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/manage.png">
		</div>
		<div class="word">（3）输入申请证书的手机号码，将会收到一条带有验证码的短信，填写验证码，并设置6位数字为个人密码，在确认口令处重复输入个人密码进行确认，点击“激活”按钮进行证书下载。</div>
		<div id="imgSecond">
			<image class="imgCerti"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/defication.png">
		</div>
		<div class="word">（4）设置签章：完成证书下载后，系统会自动提示设置签章。在此界面设置个人签名，设置完成后，证书即可正常使用。</div>
		<div id="imgFirst">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/make.png">
		</div>
		<div class="word">2、证书找回：如果曾经下载过证书，则需点击“证书找回”按钮找回证书方可使用。</div>
		<div class="word">3、点击“证书更新”中的“更新”按钮对电子证书进行更新。</div>
		<div id="imgFirst">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/update.png">
		</div>
		<div class="word">二、查看证书信息</div>
		<div class="word">1、下载好证书后，点击“我的证书”查看证书详情</div>
		<div id="imgFirst">
			<image class="img"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/certifiManage.png">
		</div>
		<div class="word">2、点击“签章管理”可对电子签名进行查看和修改。</div>
		<div id="imgFirst">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/signPic.png">
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- 待审签内容的签名和驳回  -->

	<div id="doclist">
		<div name="return" class="noticeWord">
			<返回 操作说明:
		</div>
		<div id="doclistTitle" class="title">待审签内容的签名和驳回</div>
		<div class="word">1.当存在待审签记录时，页面会在“待处理”增加提醒，点击申请上部可以进入患者详情，点击下方记录按钮进入待审签详情页</div>
		<div id="imgThird">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/docList.png">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/docListDetail.jpg">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/allRecord.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="word">2.将滑块往左滑动，将进入批改页面,输入批改意见并提交，返回上级页面</div>
		<div id="imgSecond">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/correct.jpg">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/write.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="word">3.将滑块往右滑动，输入您凭证的六位签名密码，完成通过审签</div>
		<div id="imgSecond">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/pass.jpg">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/input.jpg">
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- 已审签内容的查询  -->

	<div id="record">
		<div name="return" class="noticeWord">
			<返回 操作说明:
		</div>
		<div id="recordTitle" class="title">已审签内容的查询</div>
		<div class="word">1.当您打开APP,将进入审签记录的界面，显示当前用户的已审签记录列表</div>
		<div id="imgFirst">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/record.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="word">2.点击两边的箭头可以查看前一天和后一天的审签记录，点击时间可以进入时间选择器</div>
		<div id="imgSecond">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/select.jpg">
			<image class="img"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/selecter.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="word">3.点击左边头像可以查看患者的基本信息，在基本信息页面，点击左上方箭头返回上级页面，点击字号可以调整大小，点击左下角的导航收放按钮可以对导航进行收放显示操作</div>
		<div id="imgSecond">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/detail.jpg">
			<image class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/info.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="word">4.点击右方区域可以查看审签记录的详情</div>
		<div id="imgSecond">
			<image class="img"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/signDetail.jpg"> <image
				class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/recordDetail.jpg">
		</div>
		<div class="word">5.点击“住院记录”,"历史审批",“患者详情”可以查看相应的信息</div>
		<div id="imgThird">
			<image class="img"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/recordDetail.jpg"> <image
				class="img" src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/history.jpg">
			<image class="img"
				src="/dssweb/resource/images/download/patientDetail.jpg">
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="copyRight">
		<div id="wnCopyRight">
			<span>©山西卫宁软件有限公司</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>